Honestly a prisoner island thing would be fucking epic, Permanently banning someone doesn't solve anything, But if he manages to climb out of the toxic pit that (in theory) is a prisoner island as a reformed player, He definitely deserves a place within the normal servers.
Also I want my account back {{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}}

